bhale jodi ( kannada : ಭಲೇ ಜೋಡಿ ) is a 1970 indian kannada language drama film written and directed by y. r. swamy .   it stars rajkumar in dual roles with bharathi and dinesh in other lead roles .   the film was based on the story written by jawar seetharaman and was produced under rajkamal arts banner .   the movie was remade in telugu in 1972 as bullema bullodu and in hindi in 1973 as jaise ko taisa .